And I told my father, I went back to see him recently,

00:25:21.880 --> 00:25:24.680
I said, "Dad, I gotta go to the gym,

00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:27.660
"'cause I live in the city just to stay in shape.

00:25:27.660 --> 00:25:28.500
"How do you do it?

00:25:28.500 --> 00:25:30.260
"You're still thin."

00:25:30.260 --> 00:25:31.940
He's now 86.

00:25:31.940 --> 00:25:35.220
He said, "My farm is my gym."

00:25:35.220 --> 00:25:36.060
Oh yes.

00:25:36.060 --> 00:25:37.820
And he's out there working.

00:25:37.820 --> 00:25:41.140
And just like his father before him,

00:25:41.140 --> 00:25:43.300
who lived to age 92,

00:25:43.300 --> 00:25:47.740
my father is fit because he's working the land.

00:25:47.740 --> 00:25:50.500
So I wanted to leave my audience with that thought.

00:25:50.500 --> 00:25:52.820
Your last thought, and then I wanna say a prayer.

00:25:52.820 --> 00:25:54.820
Well, last thought is that,

00:25:54.820 --> 00:25:58.140
I think I'll hit the last period on the consumer.

00:25:58.140 --> 00:26:01.460
Literally, we have to get, the call for action

00:26:01.460 --> 00:26:04.300
is to educate them on where we are now

00:26:04.300 --> 00:26:06.460
in the industrial agriculture revolution,

00:26:06.460 --> 00:26:07.580
how we're gonna stop it,

00:26:07.580 --> 00:26:10.700
and then give the farmers a way to move forward.

00:26:10.700 --> 00:26:12.540
Because nobody's gonna give up a job

00:26:12.540 --> 00:26:14.620
and walk away from it if they can't make a living.

00:26:14.620 --> 00:26:16.100
The quality of life is still there,

00:26:16.100 --> 00:26:19.180
and that's where the young generations are gonna come

00:26:19.180 --> 00:26:19.180
in

00:26:19.180 --> 00:26:20.460
and take over those farms,

00:26:20.460 --> 00:26:22.060
'cause they're looking for a quality of life.

00:26:22.060 --> 00:26:25.140
It's not about the money, it's about quality of life,

00:26:25.140 --> 00:26:28.340
and regaining and rebuilding that family structure

00:26:28.340 --> 00:26:31.180
and the community that results from it.

00:26:31.180 --> 00:26:32.740
Let's say a prayer for those

00:26:32.740 --> 00:26:34.580
in the agriculture industry.

00:26:34.580 --> 00:26:37.260
Father in heaven, we pray for those

00:26:37.260 --> 00:26:42.260
who are producing the food that keeps us healthy.

00:26:42.260 --> 00:26:47.340
Father, we pray for your favor,

00:26:47.340 --> 00:26:50.340
for the restoration, for the regeneration

00:26:50.340 --> 00:26:54.060
of our food supply to have the best possible nutrients

00:26:54.060 --> 00:26:57.500
with the fewest possible chemicals and side effects.

00:26:57.500 --> 00:27:00.800
Jesus, that your original plan for our health

00:27:00.800 --> 00:27:03.460
would thrive through the agriculture industry.

00:27:03.460 --> 00:27:05.420
We pray this blessing on American farmers

00:27:05.420 --> 00:27:08.700
and around the world, in Jesus' name, amen.

